infoparam.value:
Below are the simplifications made when the SysML model was created
The startup procedure is not modeled. The shutdown procedure is not modeled. Maintenance is not addressed.
The controller will never fail. None of the actors will ever fail.
The controller will never run out of power.
The temperture sensor, the test button, the alarm and the cooling system will be permanently connected to the controller.
Current version of the model dos not save temperature values. Current version of the system has no disk.
